cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the application of computer vision and deep learning algorithms for skin lesion diagnosis. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning algorithms for classification and diagnosis also falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses post-processing methods for improving the accuracy of diagnosis, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the use of dermoscopic images for diagnosis falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
